{
  "texts": [
    "In this example, the triplet is \"battery life-great-positive.\"",
    "Peng et al. (2020) introduced the AOSTE task, which is addressed using a twostage framework.",
    "In the first stage, aspect terms, opinion terms, and sentiment polarity are extracted, transforming the task into two sequence labelling tasks: one for aspect terms and their corresponding sentiment polarities and another for opinion terms.",
    "In the second stage, aspect and opinion terms are paired to construct the triplets.",
    "Jet-BERT (Xu et al. 2020b) introduced an end-to-end model with a novel position-aware tagging scheme for AOSTE, achieving improved performance by jointly capturing target aspects, associated sentiments, and opinion spans in triplets."
  ]
}